Name: jupyter-saagie-plugin
Version: 1.0.6
Summary: Easily create a Saagie Python job from a Jupyter notebook
Home-page: https://github.com/saagie/jupyter-saagie-plugin
Author: Saagie
Author-email: support@saagie.com
